  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The sea piles up on the Galle Sea Road",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Several places including the Galle Sea Road and the Port Police Customs were flooded today (02) evening due to the sea waves coming ashore.",
        "Several boats parked on the shore have also washed ashore due to the waves and the sea road has been filled with water and sand, and traffic on the Galle Matara main road has been disrupted.",
        "The embankment of Samudra Mawatha has also been damaged and with the prevailing strong wind, the sea waves have flowed onto the land."
      ],
